  "texts": [
    "Proficiency in AI art enables the creation of new and exciting works (Medium.com 2023a).",
    "Acquiring programming basics: Although it is not necessary to be a professional programmer when it comes to using GPT and other AI models, basic programming knowledge can be an advantage.",
    "These skills allow us to customize and integrate the models into our applications or projects.",
    "For example, if a company is developing its GPT-based chatbot, programming fundamentals can help finetune how the chatbot works (Medium.com 2023b).",
    "APIs allow applications to communicate with other services and systems."
